title: FRAME Reintroduce `TransactionExtension` as a replacement for `SignedExtension`

doc:
  - audience: Runtime User
    description: |
      Reintroduces the changes in #2280 which were later reverted. In addition to that, this PR
      bumps the extrinsic format version to 5, as per RFC#84. For a full list of changes, please
      see the PrDoc for #2280.

